<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Thangngur</author>
<hymn_number>66</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kanaan phaizawl Saron pak hawih,
 Maa Rom miten a na thiek uh;
 * Tang khuo a ngui ie, Saron a thiek nau chu,
 Nunau a lieng ui liehkhuh ding neilo in,
 A damnau Saron pak a thiek ziekun (2) D.S

[V2]
 2. Saron pak hawih thiek sa nung khah,
 Amah lunga gulhte kawm achun;
 * Lili'n a hung pak a lunggil thim u-ah,
 A chung zawn u-ah zing Aksi'n a hung vak,
 A kim uh ah nawpna gimlim zam vel (2) D.S

[V3]
 3. Saron pak na hawih zo nai puoi,
 Mal gam tangpi thim sung ahin chu;
 * Lummei a kai ie Na pak hawih sel ding in,
 Nisan hung vakin na sakmel hung lang hen,
 Tichun na hawih zie chu hun he tanau (2) D.S

[V4]
 4. Kanaan phaizawl Saron pak hawih,
 Judai gamah hung pak lun kitin;
 * Zalen a nuom tau thilsiem chitin chengte,
 Ngaiin a hun thil ui, liengthei lei miten,
 Israelte'n le hun na lawp tan au. (2) D.S

[V5]
 5. Aw Saron pak hun muh ka nuom,
 Van lopi a Na hung pak ding chu;
 * Kichamna thing a na bawt na mun achun;
 Hung thuom in natin nawplenna lopi in,
 Sa leh mihiem kigalna bei tana.(2) D.S</lyrics>
<title>Kanaan Phaizawl</title>
</song>